Official Channels Day is on June 7, 2025 

What does this mean? Channels were launched on June 7, 2023 and quickly became cozy corners for creators, curators and communities to connect and grow on Farcaster.

Celebrate with us!

If you're a channel owner, quote cast this post with a note about why you started your channel. How is it meaningful to you? And don't forget to celebrate your active members by tagging the top contributors and letting them know how they help make your cozy corner better.

If you don't own a channel, or are simply a fan of channels, quote cast this post, tag your top three channels, and share why they‚Äôre important to you. How do they make the Internet (or Farcaster) a better place for you?

The P/E ratio according to their 2024 earnings is around 115 right now 

For comparison, Nvidia‚Äôs P/E ratio in Spring 2023 hovered around the same level with the AI boom

cast.text:
The Circle IPO seems to be overvalued bc there‚Äôs so much demand for exposure to stablecoin growth and there‚Äôs not many options to get exposure, especially for more traditional investors 

Coinbase gets 100% of the revenue from $USDC held on its platform. 50% for all other residual revenue from $USDC reserves 

Coinbase is better placed to earn from the gain in USDC market cap than Circle itself us. 

This will be true for the next few years at minimum. According to Coinbase‚Äôs 2024 report, the agreement that began in 2022 runs for an initial term of three years. 

After that, Coinbase and Circle will ‚Äúdiscuss in good faith whether any modifications to the Circle Agreement are warranted.‚Äù If no new terms are agreed upon, the deal automatically renews for another three years‚Äîunless either side fails to meet its obligations.

With all of that said, Circle could essentially become a meme stock for stablecoin growth and get a valuation far beyond its current fundamentals
